{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSInteger","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSInteger"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"badge","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The current application badge number (0 to clear badge).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"badge"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Reports the current badge count to Pushwoosh for analytics and to enable"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"badge-based segmentation. This is useful for:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Analytics"}]},{"text":": Track user engagement through unread counts","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Segmentation"}]},{"text":": Target users with high\/low badge counts","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Badge management"}]},{"text":": Allow server-side badge manipulation","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method whenever you update the app badge to keep Pushwoosh in sync."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sync badge with Pushwoosh when updating unread counts:"}]},{"code":["class NotificationBadgeManager {","","    private(set) var unreadCount: Int = 0 {","        didSet {","            updateBadge()","        }","    }","","    func markAsRead(_ notificationIds: [String]) {","        unreadCount = max(0, unreadCount - notificationIds.count)","    }","","    func handleNewNotification() {","        unreadCount += 1","    }","","    func clearAll() {","        unreadCount = 0","    }","","    private func updateBadge() {","        \/\/ Update system badge","        if #available(iOS 16.0, *) {","            UNUserNotificationCenter.current().setBadgeCount(unreadCount)","        } else {","            UIApplication.shared.applicationIconBadgeNumber = unreadCount","        }","","        \/\/ Sync with Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(unreadCount)","    }","}","","\/\/ Usage in AppDelegate","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func applicationDidBecomeActive(_ application: UIApplication) {","        \/\/ Sync current badge state when app becomes active","        let currentBadge = application.applicationIconBadgeNumber","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(currentBadge)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)sendBadges:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"sendBadges:","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendBadges:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Synchronizes the application badge number with Pushwoosh servers."}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendbadges:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/sendBadges:":{"kind":"symbol","title":"sendBadges:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendBadges:","abstract":[{"text":"Synchronizes the application badge number with Pushwoosh servers.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendbadges:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"}}}